Usage:
  utility_name -a <p1>
  utility_name -bP2
  utility_name -c <p3>  # -c not bound.
  utility_name -d <p4>...
  utility_name -eP5...

  utility_name --long-1=<g1>
  utility_name --long-2 <g2>
  utility_name --long-3=<g3>...

  utility_name -f|--long-4

Options:
  -a <p1>
	-b P2
  -d <p4>
  -e P5
  --long-2=<g2>
	-f,--long-4
